    "description": "<p>An Established Electrical Engineering Contractor (Grade L6) at Tagore Industrial / Upper Thomson &nbsp;&nbsp;We are a Design and Build mechanical and electrical (“M&amp;E”) engineering contractor in Singapore and we have been established in Singapore for over 25 years. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Will Do, Can Do. On time, Every time. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We aspire to complete our tasks as expected and generate benefits for all stakeholders, always. We strive to grow with integrity and nurture our growth with sustainability.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Specialties: M&amp;E, Building Development, Construction, Design and Build, and Safety and Quality</p>",
